data.description: Model Home! Located in Oakhurst Glen, a premier swim and tennis subdivision in the growing city of South Fulton. Penwell 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom floorplan home. Front flex room, perfect for home office. Cozy family room with fireplace! Kitchen features exquisitely crafted cabinets with decorative crown molding, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Luxury RevWood by Mohawk wood plank flooring throughout most of main living areas. Large upstairs loft. Primary suite offers a deluxe bath with tile shower, separate soaker tub.
